{"title":"Cynllun Iaith Gymraeg Cofrestrfa Tir EM","public_updated_at":"2016-04-27T08:00:00Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Mae Deddf yr Iaith Gymraeg 1993 yn gosod dyletswydd ar bob corff sector cyhoeddus i drin y Gymraeg a’r Saesneg yn gyfartal wrth ddarparu gwasanaethau i’r cyhoedd yng Nghymru. O ganlyniad, mae Cofrestrfa Tir EM wedi paratoi Cynllun iaith Gymraeg Cofrestrfa Tir EM o dan adran 21(3) y ddeddf a chafodd ei gymeradwyo’n llawn gan Fwrdd yr Iaith Gymraeg ym Mawrth 1998.</p>\n\n<p>Cymeradwywyd yr ail argraffiad yn Ionawr 2002, y trydydd yn Chwefror 2005 a’r pedwerydd ym Mawrth 2010.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2016-04-27T09:00:00.000+01:00","note":"Added translation"}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_2042633\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/publications/hm-land-registry-welsh-language-scheme/2042633\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/assets/pub-cover-html-b0465911e56983d98c70f0e25fba24bc206d37e8c83d4addf6421dcf6022c6cd.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/publications/hm-land-registry-welsh-language-scheme/2042633\">Cynllun Iaith Gymraeg Cofrestrfa Tir EM</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"type\">HTML</span>\n    </p>\n\n\n  </div>\n</section>"],"emphasised_organisations":["5c54ae52-341b-499e-a6dd-67f04633b8cf"],"national_applicability":{"england":{"label":"England","applicable":true},"northern_ireland":{"label":"Northern Ireland","applicable":false,"alternative_url":""},"scotland":{"label":"Scotland","applicable":false,"alternative_url":""},"wales":{"label":"Wales","applicable":true}},"political":false,"government":{"title":"2015 Conservative government","slug":"2015-conservative-government","current":true},"tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]},"first_public_at":"2016-04-27T09:00:00.000+01:00"}